divs: Sighting DetailsSitting in the hot tub in the back yard and seen the object. It was similar tothe same as we seen a couple weeks ago. The only difference were the lights. They looked white. This time we seen it flying in the overcast. Last time itwas Clear skies. Seen it in the East to South East and it headed North thenTook a turn to the NW. Opposite direction as we seen a couple weeks ago. Wasthe same boomerang wing shape with at least 40 lights on it. We would like toknow if anyone else has seen the same shape.
